span>\n                  <span class=\"loadingError\"><\/span>\n                <\/span>\n                <span class=\"greyText\">&nbsp;|&nbsp;<\/span>\n                <span class=\"loadingLinkSpan\">\n                  <a class=\"actionLinkLite loadingLink\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-keep-on-success=\"true\" data-remote=\"true\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"new Ajax.Request(&#39;/book/reviews/35297311-they-come-in-all-colors?rating=3&#39;, {asynchronous:true, evalScripts:true, method:&#39;get&#39;, parameters:&#39;authenticity_token=&#39; + encodeURIComponent(&#39;sAMqtsHa+9zkv8Ln+F8spk7AwOdhRHYMDgK95tVfFfJTEdgb/A/1vjMP9Rvgn2jlo5gcxQjv2RktL2XPAnQZOQ==&#39;)}); return false;\">3 stars <span class=\"greyText\">(88)<\/span><\/a>\n                  <span class=\"loadingAnimation\"><\/span>\n                  <span class=\"loadingError\"><\/span>\n                <\/span>\n                <span class=\"greyText\">&nbsp;|&nbsp;<\/span>\n                <span class=\"loadingLinkSpan\">\n                  <a class=\"actionLinkLite loadingLink\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-keep-on-success=\"true\" data-remote=\"true\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"new Ajax.Request(&#39;/book/reviews/35297311-they-come-in-all-colors?rating=2&#39;, {asynchronous:true, evalScripts:true, method:&#39;get&#39;, parameters:&#39;authenticity_token=&#39; + encodeURIComponent(&#39;ccdw2VBIshDP0icQ+vjSDf10t1a8M/bqnLkgOfXJevCS1YJ0bZ28chhiEOziOJZOECxrdNWYWf+/lPgQIuJ2Ow==&#39;)}); return false;\">2 stars <span class=\"greyText\">(34)<\/span><\/a>\n                  <span class=\"loadingAnimation\"><\/span>\n                  <span class=\"loadingError\"><\/span>\n                <\/span>\n                <span class=\"greyText\">&nbsp;|&nbsp;<\/span>\n                <span class=\"loadingLinkSpan\">\n                  <a class=\"actionLinkLite loadingLink\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-keep-on-success=\"true\" data-remote=\"true\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"new Ajax.Request(&#39;/book/reviews/35297311-they-come-in-all-colors?rating=1&#39;, {